釋法?<br />\n啲大陸住嘅藍絲可唔可以dq"},{"pid":"c58ad87901e83537a283d66217cbd1e9d5d81ae8","tid":2137333,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"8點半至10點，企係金鐘，太子，旺角站望一次再同我講嘢"},{"pid":"12ae8ef97536b3e09640a6bbc3cef7e824e1b01c","tid":2137333,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:40:08.000Z","msg":"遲啲朴野都係聚集？<br />\n展開大規模坐監？<br />\n呢個老不死知唔知自己講緊乜"},{"pid":"903bdbe3143e52ff0d0a0d5eee703b90e868a8d9","tid":2137333,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"有一年時間去諗點樣對付市民，點解唔用一年時間去解決民生？<br />\n所以市民點解咁憎共產黨其實有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歷史以來講俾我地聽，無一個朝代政府係鬥得贏人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93c4513d2444c4887415c3393d68c9af612a6a0","tid":2137333,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"立條法用兩個月，set 個票站用一年<br />\n<br />\n果然蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"4967e2a1e45ddfaba9ef577331f353b1dced0a84","tid":2137333,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74055064c3059e5104fe3385d119d8f31a106e83","tid":2137333,"uid":364767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"邊條法例禁止人群聚集？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"緊急法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d077eb24401f750a3e3a60cded684c3919abc1","tid":2137333,"uid":300644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"嘩！用成年去研究，睇嚟呢個研究將會對人類發展有重大影響"},{"pid":"6344388b013eefd010c950b44eea0132787d2ecd","tid":2137333,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"網上投票，街站投票，講低一聲都可投票。<br />\n<br />\n選前定好結果， 支援大灣區選民，支援長期不在港的人投票。非選民都可投。好似早排街站有300萬人簽名支持咁。"}]}